@pulkit.maheshwari.319 proposed to @nehabhandari_2490 10 years ago in GIP foodcourt. He recreated the same event after 10 years, same place, same way just few days before wedding. But then Neha thought why should always boys make an extra effort to make their partner happy, this time I’ll do something. Her photographer knocked at Pulkit's door and handed over the clues, one by one, she planned the entire day. He was supposed to solve the riddles to reach next destination. 
We mean tell us if you’re not loving this idea?
